-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/s0cOgZxvlGY.png\"/><p>拉丁學名：Comptonia peregrina\n</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E6%BC%82%E6%B3%8A%E9%A6%99%E8%95%A8%E6%9C%A8comptonie-voyageuse---%E7%94%9C%E8%95%A8","title":"漂泊香蕨木comptonie voyageuse - 甜蕨","date_modified":"2023-03-14T07:37:55Z"},{"id":"%E7%86%8F%E9%99%B8%E9%A6%99%EF%BC%8D%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E6%91%A9%E6%B4%9B%E5%93%A5%E6%9E%9D%E8%91%89%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B6%E6%96%82%E6%84%9F","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/cOqlgJw1MFY.jpg\"/><p>科屬：漆樹科黃連木屬\n產地：以摩洛哥地區、地中海沿岸為主要集中地\n英文俗名：Mastic\n拉丁學名：Pistacia lentiscus\n中文其他俗名：乳香脂、乳香黃連木\n精油萃取方法：蒸餾法\n精油萃油部位：枝葉為大宗、少部份以樹脂萃取\n</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E7%86%8F%E9%99%B8%E9%A6%99%EF%BC%8D%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E6%91%A9%E6%B4%9B%E5%93%A5%E6%9E%9D%E8%91%89%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B6%E6%96%82%E6%84%9F","title":"熏陸香－來自摩洛哥枝葉的收斂感","date_modified":"2023-03-14T07:36:07Z"},{"id":"%E7%93%8A%E5%B4%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%A3%A0","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/kmswgpwk2_X.jpg\"/><p>瓊崖海棠，學名：Calophyllum inophyllum，源自東南亞，目前在大洋洲地區許多島嶼上都能看見它的蹤跡，在我們台灣也不少。而在法屬的玻里尼西亞，當地人自古以來就將瓊崖海棠視為一種神聖植物，他們認為與皮膚有關的任何問題，不論是擦傷、疤痕、燙傷、燙傷、感染，都可以用瓊崖海棠油治療。</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E7%93%8A%E5%B4%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%A3%A0","title":"瓊崖海棠","date_modified":"2023-03-14T07:34:51Z"},{"id":"%E9%87%8E%E8%96%84%E8%8D%B7","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/kgRLhZHZH-X.jpg\"/><p>＊拉丁學名：Mentha arvensis</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E9%87%8E%E8%96%84%E8%8D%B7","title":"野薄荷","date_modified":"2023-03-14T07:32:58Z"},{"id":"%E8%97%8D%E8%86%A0%E5%B0%A4%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/UK_Jh5MYH-X.jpg\"/><p>＊拉丁學名：Eucalyptus globulus</p>","url":"https://yuanliu