-84a2-49051586f893/8SPLh5qQ98X.jpg\"/><p>生命就像一本書。</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E6%87%B7","title":"真正的關懷","date_modified":"2023-02-04T06:01:05Z"},{"id":"les-fleurs-%C3%A9ternelles-%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%E4%B9%8B%E8%8A%B1","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/0XsJhpSP98X.jpg\"/><p>文／吳思皓</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/les-fleurs-%C3%A9ternelles-%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%E4%B9%8B%E8%8A%B1","title":"Les  fleurs  éternelles  永恒之花","date_modified":"2023-02-04T03:16:02Z"},{"id":"%E5%86%AC%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/80pJh5RP98X.png\"/><p>文／Megan</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E5%86%AC%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD","title":"冬日裡的小太陽","date_modified":"2023-02-04T03:14:54Z"},{"id":"%E8%90%8A%E5%A7%86","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/4hpbg5ItB9X.jpg\"/><p>科別：芸香科\n學名：Citrus latifolia、Citrus limetta\n英名：Lime\n其他中名：白檸檬、無籽檸檬\n主要產地：中美、南歐\n萃取方式/部位：蒸餾、壓榨 / 果皮\n成份：檸檬烯、牻牛兒醛、香茅醛、萜烯酯類、(呋喃)香豆素類…等</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E8%90%8A%E5%A7%86","title":"萊姆","date_modified":"2023-02-04T03:13:50Z"},{"id":"%E8%B2%93%E7%B2%89%E5%88%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%B3%E9%A6%99%E7%85%A7%E8%AD%B7-1","html_content":"<img src=\"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/248826cd-18b5-4b59-84a2-49051586f893/4o1tgJz788X.jpg\"/><p>怎麽？貓也會長粉刺的嗎？貓粉刺的原因不明，但通常發生於成年或老年貓身上，幼貓較少發生，多見於下巴部位，偶爾也會出現在尾巴位置上，患處初時會出現黑色分泌物，就像我們的黑頭粉刺般，密密麻麻的堵在下巴位置，假如有繼發性感染，就會形成毛囊炎或癤病，出現下巴腫大的情況。</p>","url":"https://yuanliuschool.com/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/f/%E8%B2%93%E7%B2%89%E5%88%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%B3%E9%A6%99%E7%85%A7%E8%AD%B7-1","title":"貓粉刺的芳香照護","date_modified":"2023-02-04T03:12:26Z"},{"id":"%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%A